All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Board
Represents the game board of Splendor.
Card
Abstract class representing a generic card and all data associated with it.
Deck
Represents a deck of cards which can hold vanilla cards, nobles, or orient cards.
DeckType
Represents the type of deck.
Game
Represents the game type.
Launcher
This class launches spring and detects the necessary controllers.
LobbyService
This class deals with the Lobby Service functions.
Manager
Controls each game of splendor.
Noble
A class which represents a Noble in the game of splendor.
Player
Represents each player information.
Rank
Represents the rank of each card.
Rest
A test Rest controller for Splendor game.
Splendor
Represents a game of splendor and data associated with it.
Token
Represents the token types.
VanillaCard
Represents a basic vanilla card which is part of the original game.
